	     *        For use by methods creating specific types of FArrays.
	     *        
	     * This implementation only applies builder to the single expression of this 
	     * ScalarAsArray.
	     * 
	     * @see #buildLiteral(boolean)
	     * @see #buildScalarized(java.util.Map,FExp)
	     */
